Interface Getter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlertPresent, AlertText, BodyText, CookieByName, CookiePresent, CurrentUrl, ElementAttribute, ElementPresent, ElementSelected, ElementStyle, ElementValue, Eval, PageSource, Text, TextPresent, Title

    public interface Getter
    Interface to plug into the generic Assert/Verify/Store steps that does the work of actually getting the relevant variable.
